g(x):=\log\bigl(f(x)\bigr)=\sum_{k=2}^n k\log(1+x_k)
\Phi(x,\lambda):=g(x)-\lambda\prod_{k=2}^n x_k
{\partial\Phi\over\partial x_k}=0\quad(2\leq k\leq n),\qquad \prod_{k=2}^n x_k=1\ .
{k\over 1+x_k}={\lambda\over x_k}\qquad(2\leq k\leq n)\tag{1}
x_k={\lambda\over k-\lambda}\ ,
\prod_{k=2}^n(1+x_k)={n!\over\lambda^{n-1}}\ .
